com.interpss.se

Interface SEBus

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseAclfBus<SEGen,SELoad>, Bus, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAclfBus, IAclfBusAdaptation, IAclfBusAdjustment, IAclfBusFunc, IAclfBusZeroZFunc, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SEBusImpl

    public interface SEBus
extends BaseAclfBus<SEGen,SELoad>
    A representation of the model object 'Bus'. SE Bus class

    The following features are supported:

    • PSe Bus Rec
    • QSe Bus Rec
    • Volt Se Rec
    • Volt JMatrix Index
    See Also:
    SEPackage.getSEBus()
